	* /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/commands/Makefile.raw, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/commands/mmimport.raw, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/include/config.inc, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/include/config.raw, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/include/functions.inc, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/include/functions.raw, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/www/Makefile.raw, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/Documentation/Overview.txt, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/Makefile, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/README, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/changelog, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/config, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/configure, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/mmimport:
	Created a Makefile for convenience

	Added a file named "config". configure parses it and creates Makefiles
	and sed-scripts out of it's content.

	New Installation-Method:

	 - vi config

	 - make

	 - make install
	     as "root"

	Directory-Cleanup

2000-11-01  michael  <michael@ruf098>

	* /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/include/functions.inc: Foo

