	suite and some notes about the database-layout.

	* /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/include/functions.inc, /cvsroot/koch-suite/src/mmimport:
	fixed a problem with importing Recipes, that have no empty line
	between a ingredient-line and a header for additional ingredients.

